 tracked by the DOJ for refusing to let their children be educated that the drag andtransgender lifestyleis normal.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"the DOJ\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"their children\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"the drag andtransgender\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a presumptive Presidential nominee, Kamala notJoe, who kicked off part of her campaign by appearing on Ru Paul's drag show just the other day.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2249, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"score\": 0.999949812248612, \"rank\": 4.322511858604196e-05, \"text\": \"Kamala\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\"}, {\"begin\": 2316, \"end\": 2323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RuPaul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ru Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RuPaul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RuPaul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a presumptive Presidential nominee\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"her campaign\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"https://twitter.com/RuPaulsDragRace/status/1816518934939742353 Fitting since she's evidently an honorarysex worker?We have politicians trying to normalize that which is NOT normal or moral.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"https://twitter.com/RuPaulsDragRace/status/1816518934939742353 Fitting\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"an honorarysex worker?We\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2474},